<db:para>Qt provides powerful graphics engine that supports easy visualization of items, with support for rotation and zooming. Additionally it provides an event propagation architecture for interaction.</db:para>
<db:para>These examples demonstrate the fundamental aspects of canvas programming with Qt.</db:para>
<db:variablelist role="examples-graphicsview">
